---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Healthcare industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Healthcare systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Deal Sourcing -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Patient Intake & Onboarding" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Patient Intake & Onboarding</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated patient intake that captures complete information from first contact—demographics, insurance, medical history, allergies—in a single, unified record. Reduces intake time from 45+ minutes to under 10 minutes while ensuring accuracy.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated intake form capture</li>
            <li>Insurance verification automation</li>
            <li>Medical history aggregation</li>
            <li>Allergy and medication reconciliation</li>
            <li>Real-time eligibility checking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Underwriting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Clinical Workflow Automation" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Clinical Workflow Automation</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Intelligent automation that connects clinical teams, reduces manual handoffs, and surfaces patient priorities in real-time. Automates routine documentation, task routing, and escalation so clinicians focus on care delivery.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated clinical documentation</li>
            <li>Task routing and prioritization</li>
            <li>Provider-to-provider coordination</li>
            <li>Patient queue management</li>
            <li>Real-time clinical alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Appointment & Scheduling Optimization" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Appointment & Scheduling Optimization</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified scheduling system that matches patient demand to provider availability, optimizes appointment duration, and reduces no-shows through automated confirmations and reminders. Increases appointment fill rates and reduces wasted capacity.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Provider availability optimization</li>
            <li>Automated appointment confirmations</li>
            <li>No-show prediction and prevention</li>
            <li>Multi-location scheduling</li>
            <li>Real-time capacity visibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Insurance & Revenue Cycle" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Insurance & Revenue Cycle</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated insurance verification that checks eligibility in real-time, pre-authorizes services before care delivery, and flags coverage issues before they become denials. Reduces insurance-related delays and improves claim acceptance rates.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Real-time eligibility verification</li>
            <li>Automated pre-authorization</li>
            <li>Claims tracking and follow-up</li>
            <li>Denial prevention and analysis</li>
            <li>Revenue cycle metrics dashboard</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buyer Profile Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Clinical Outcomes & Quality Metrics" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Clinical Outcomes & Quality Metrics</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time visibility into patient outcomes, quality metrics, and clinical performance across providers and departments. Track readmission rates, patient satisfaction, treatment effectiveness, and compliance with clinical guidelines.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Patient outcome tracking</li>
            <li>Quality metric dashboards</li>
            <li>Readmission and complication monitoring</li>
            <li>Provider performance analytics</li>
            <li>Compliance and regulatory reporting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Market Intelligence -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Patient Communication & Engagement" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Patient Communication & Engagement</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified patient communication platform that manages appointment reminders, pre-visit questionnaires, post-visit follow-up, and secure messaging. Increases patient engagement and reduces no-shows while improving satisfaction scores.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated appointment reminders</li>
            <li>Pre-visit questionnaires</li>
            <li>Post-visit follow-up workflows</li>
            <li>Secure patient messaging</li>
            <li>Patient education and engagement tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>

